data.text:
This is my stylized tribute to the Pakistani Legend Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan often referred to as the ‘Shahenshah-e-Qawwali’ or the 'King of Qawwali. He was a legendary Pakistani musician. whose soul-stirring voice transcended cultural and geographical boundaries.

More Renders https://www.artstation.com/artwork/6N2J35

Instagram https://www.instagram.com/khatri3d/

Youtube : https://www.youtube.com/khatri3d

Thank you !

Good job !

I am so glad to see him again …

I am going to listen to him right now.
